              These results demonstrate the achievement of timed assembly and disassembly of a material and the power of predictive modeling to identify the appropriate region of phase space to achieve this engineering feat. To further demonstrate the oscillatory nature of the assembly, we extend the timescale of simulations out to 48 h over which we expect to capture an additional assembly oscillation. As shown in Fig. 
              5G, H
              , we observe a similar oscillation in connectivity and clustering index as in the first 24 h, with similar dependence on 



                    n

